VALUES
  ('medical-tech-moex-21038', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關單純 疹病毒（Herpes simplex virus）之敘述，何者是錯誤的？ 是DNA病毒 外套膜蛋白質gC可與細胞上之受體（receptor）結合 早期基因產生之mRNA可生成gC等結構蛋白質 其外套膜是在經由核膜苞出（budding）時形成的', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21039', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '用來區分Herpes simple virus第一型及第二型的單株抗體，主要是認識其何種蛋白？ 迅早期（immediate early）蛋白  早期（early）蛋白 晚期（late）蛋白    tegument蛋白', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21040', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '帶狀 疹（shingles）是由下列何種病毒引起的？ Poxvirus    Herpes simplex virus type 1 Herpes simplex virus type 2  Varicella zoster virus', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21041', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '腸病毒的種類很多，在目前單株抗體不多的情況下，傳統上是利用何種方法來鑑定培養出的腸病毒？ neutralization test    immunofluorescence assay hemagglutination inhibition test  immunoperoxidase staining', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21042', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於腸病毒（Enterovirus）之敘述，何者為正確？ 1M MgCl 無法使得腸病毒具耐熱性  是雙股RNA病毒 2 同一型腸病毒可能引起多種疾病  病毒在pH 3～5的情況下不穩定', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21043', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關痘病毒（Poxvirus）的敘述，何者為誤？ 痘病毒是感染人類最大的DNA病毒 痘病毒在電子顯微鏡下呈啞鈴或磚塊形構造 痘病毒的DNA複製在細胞核進行 牛痘病毒（Vaccinia virus）可用來作為疫苗以防治天花', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21044', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種病毒，在一般細胞培養的狀態下，不會產生細胞病變（cytopathic effect）？ Human herpes virus type 8   Adenovirus type 2 Coxsackievirus B4    herpes simplex virus type 2', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21045', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下何種病毒通常不感染眼睛？ Herpes simplex virus typeⅠ  Human cytomegalovirus Adenovirus typeⅡ    Coxsackievirus B2', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 52, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
